title: Russian lawmakers to examine U.S. counter sanctions on May 15 - Ifax
text:
April 16, 2018 / 12:31 PM / Updated an hour ago Russian lawmakers to examine U.S. counter sanctions on May 15 - Ifax Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
MOSCOW, April 16 (Reuters) - Russia’s lower house of parliament will begin examining legislation in retaliation against new U.S. sanctions on May 15, the Interfax news agency reported citing the parliament’s council. 
Lawmakers of the State Duma will vote in the first reading of the law next month, the news agency reported. (Reporting by Maxim Rodionov Editing by Alison Williams)
